claim:
To illustrate the use of our methodology for risk prediction we depict the predicted cumulative incidence function of death from bladder cancer and other causes, for a 68-year old patient who is fully active and who was assigned to the 1/3 dose BCG group, along with the equal-precision and Hall–Wellner-type simultaneous 95% confidence bands, in Figure 2 of the Electronic Supplementary Material.Concluding remarks
In this article we proposed a computationally efficient MPPLE method for the semiparametric proportional cause-specific hazards model under incompletely observed cause of failure.
